decks.notes: This deck focuses on putting pressure on the opponent by playing aggressive creatures such as Spiteful Hexmage and Hopeless Nightmare, while also controlling the board with removal spells like Go for the Throat. The deck utilizes a mix of black and white mana sources, along with a touch of blue, to cast its powerful spells and creatures efficiently. By combining aggression with disruption, this deck aims to quickly overwhelm the opponent and secure a victory before they have a chance to stabilize.
